###
## getAllDirectores() mostrar lista de todos los directores
GET http://localhost:8090/api/v1/directores HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json



###
## getPeliculasDirectores() obtindrer directors per id
GET http://localhost:8090/api/v1/directores/8/info HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

###
## Crear director (POST)
POST http://localhost:8090/api/v1/directores HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"nombre": "Martin Scorsese",
	"nacionalidad": "USA"
}


###
## Actualizar director (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:8090/api/v1/directores/5 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"nombre": "Juan Antonio Bayona",
	"nacionalidad": "España"
}
###
## getPeliculasDirectores() obtindrer directors per id
GET http://localhost:8090/api/v1/directores/5/info HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

###
## deleteDirector
DELETE http://localhost:8090/api/v1/directores/12 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json



